jodd.log

Interface Logger

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JCLLogger, JDKLogger, Log4j2Logger, NOPLogger, SimpleLogger, Slf4jLogger

    public interface Logger
    Simple Logger interface. It defines only logger methods with string argument as our coding style and approach insist in always using if block around the logging.
